text: Mitrella dartevelli is a species of sea snail in the family Columbellidae, the dove snails. ==Description== The shell grows to a length of 9.5 mm ==Distribution== This species is distributed in the Atlantic Ocean along Gabon. ==References== * Knudsen J. (1956) Marine prosobranchs of tropical West Africa (Stenoglossa). Atlantide Report 4:7–110, 4 pls. dartevelli Category:Gastropods described in 1956
title: Mitrella dartevelli
